OL,7,FFour British people have died within a
OL,8,Fperiod of four months after being
OL,9,Fstruck down with stomach bugs while
OL,10,Fholidaying in Cape Verde, according to
OL,11,Flawyers representing their families.
OL,13,FElena Walsh, 64, from Birmingham, Mark
OL,14,FAshley, 55, of Bedfordshire, 64-year-
OL,15,Fold Karen Pooley, from Gloucester, and
OL,16,Fa 56-year-old man all died last year
OL,17,Fafter contracting severe gastric
OL,18,Fillnesses while on the island.
