OL,7,FThe retired mother-of-two became sick
OL,8,Fon October 11 with gastric symptoms
OL,9,Fincluding diarrhoea, and in the early
OL,10,Fhours of the next day, she slipped on
OL,11,Fwater leaking from a fridge while
OL,12,Fgoing to the bathroom.
OL,14,FShe was transferred to a local clinic,
OL,15,Fand over the next four days, Ms Pooley
OL,16,Fcontinued to experience diarrhoea and
OL,17,Fvomiting, alongside severe pain from
OL,18,Fher fractured femur.
