OL,7,FThe 64-year-old was airlifted to
OL,8,FTenerife for urgent care on October 16
OL,9,Fand died in the early hours of the
OL,10,Fnext day, lawyers said.
OL,12,FHer husband Andy, 62, said: "We're
OL,13,Futterly heartbroken. Karen was the
OL,14,Fkindest, loveliest person.
OL,16,F"She was a devoted wife and mum who
OL,17,Floved swimming, walking the dog in the
OL,18,FForest of Dean, and volunteered at a
OL,19,Flocal charity shop. She was also a
OL,20,Fwonderful friend who lit up every room
OL,21,Fshe entered."
