OL,7,F"In my experience, I'm used to
OL,8,Fsupporting holidaymakers who have
OL,9,Ffallen ill at resorts across the
OL,10,Fglobe, but I've never seen repeated
OL,11,Fand continued illness outbreaks at the
OL,12,Fsame resorts on such a scale over such
OL,13,Fa period of time.
OL,15,F"It's almost incomprehensible that
OL,16,Fholidaymakers continue to describe the
OL,17,Fhygiene issues at these Cape Verde
OL,18,Fhotels year-after-year. Each case
OL,19,Fisn't a statistic; it's a human story
OL,20,Fof how lives have been turned upside
OL,21,Fdown.
