OL,7,FThe UK Foreign Office issued a warning
OL,8,Fin December about the potential of
OL,9,FShigella sonnei infections in
OL,10,Ftravellers.
OL,12,FAn investigation by the UK Health
OL,13,FSecurity Agency is underway to see if
OL,14,Fthere has been a spike in cases.
OL,16,FShigella infections are caused by
OL,17,Fbacteria that can cause severe
OL,18,Fdiarrhoea, fever, and stomach cramps.
OL,19,FMost people who come down with it
OL,20,Frecover within a week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
